nodes.text: A battle at Paqualis III was a engagement during the New Republic liberation campaign after the Battle of Endor. The New Republic sent a fleet from Brentaal IV, liberated two years ago, to the Hydian Way in order to access the Core Worlds. After a series of victory, the New Republic progress was stopped by Grand Moff Zsinj.
